   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>¶ To the Chri<g ref="char:EOLunhyphen"/>stian Reader.</head>
   <l>
      <seg rend="decorInit">H</seg>Aue here (gentle reader) a thinge verie small</l>
   <l>In vtter aparaunce (as thou maiest wel see)</l>
   <l>And yet in effecte it conteineth all</l>
   <l>That Christ in his Gospel requi<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>reth of the,</l>
   <l>Wherfore as a miroure or glasse let it bee,</l>
   <l>Wherin thou maist se thine owne Image plaine,</l>
   <l>And haue therby cause thy luste to restraine.</l>
</div>
